name: Enspira Online
blurb: A Non-Violent MMO with the goal to build a Global Community and bring Fun, Safe, Inspiring Gaming to People of All Ages!

rewards.reward: ALL backers will be commemorated on a special web page on the official Enspira Online website in appreciation for showing support for this project.

All the previous rewards above PLUS...

Exclusive access to play the game during the invitation-only Closed Beta as well as access to contribute to the private Closed Beta community on the Enspira Online Forums.

Closed Beta is currently scheduled to start on or before October 29, 2013.  It will use the Windows game client.

All the previous rewards above PLUS...

Join the elite group of Internal Alpha Testers and play the game after proof of backing this project! You won't have to wait for Closed Beta to start before playing the game!

This reward will be available on or before  August 27, 2013.

Additionally, your name will be permanently enshrined in the game credits for all players to see for the life of the service.

All the previous rewards above PLUS...

Help choose the names of the individual Gnomes of Enspira. 

Names will be submitted by this group and put through a multi-round voting process where the most popular names are selected.  Runner-up names will be kept in reserve as more Gnomes are added to Enspira.  I will have final approval of all names to ensure they are appropriate for people of all ages.

All the previous rewards above PLUS...

Your name and optional picture and inspirational quote of your choosing will periodically be briefly displayed in-game during map switching sequences as an Honored Supporter for the life of the service. 


Name, picture and quote can be updated at any time by your request. Inspirational quotes must be approved by me and appropriate to be viewed by all ages.

All the previous rewards above PLUS...

Join the elite group that will decide the names of every Community within Enspira.

Every player has the opportunity to own and construct their very own island in Enspira Online and will choose a Community that they will call home. You will have the opportunity to name the Community that all the players will call home!

Names will be chosen through a multi-round voting process where the most popular names as chosen by this group will become the official Community names within Enspira.  Runner-up names will be kept in reserve as Enspira grows and adds more Communities. I will have final approval of all names to ensure they are appropriate for viewing by people of all ages.

All the previous rewards above PLUS...

A special tribute to you will appear periodically as a Featured Honored Supporter on the game client login screen (including future platform upgrades such as Mac, Linux, iPhone, iPad, Android, and OUYA) and on the front page of the official Enspira Online website.  The featured tribute will include your name, picture and inspirational quote of your choice for the life of the service. 


Name, picture and quote can be updated at any time by your request. Inspirational quotes must be approved by me and appropriate to be viewed by all ages.

All the previous rewards above PLUS...\r\n\r\nReceive a one-of-a-kind, personally signed, numbered and professionally printed, matted and framed piece of actual code that is used to operate Enspira Online.  That's right, own a piece of the very computer code that brings this game to life!  No two code prints are alike; each person will receive a completely different piece of code.  Frame color and type preferences can be emailed prior to construction to help coordinate with your home decor.
